Comes in a hefty 6. 1-oz. weight for added durability. Shoulder-to-shoulder taping helps prevent raveling and rip-out. Full cut assures roomy comfort. Soft pure cotton feels terrific all day long. Comes in a hefty 6. 1-oz. weight for added durability. Shoulder-to-shoulder taping helps prevent raveling and rip-out. Full cut assures roomy comfort. Soft pure cotton feels terrific all day long. Comes in a hefty 6. 1-oz. weight for added durability. Shoulder-to-shoulder taping helps prevent raveling and rip-out. Full cut assures roomy comfort. Soft pure cotton feels terrific all day long. Comes in a hefty 6. 1-oz. weight for added durability. Shoulder-to-shoulder taping helps prevent raveling and rip-out. Full cut assures roomy comfort. Soft pure cotton feels terrific all day long.
